General Assembly Of North Carolina Session 2025
1 Big Rock Blue Marlin
2 Tournament $10 $20 0 0
3 Birthplace of American
4 Independence $10 $20 0 0
5 Boy Scouts of America
6 …."
7 SECTION 5. G.S. 20-81.12 is amended by adding a new subsection to read:
8 "() Birthplace of American Independence. – The Division shall transfer quarterly the
9 money in the Collegiate and Cultural Attraction Plate Account derived from the sale of
10 "Birthplace of American Independence" plates to Halifax County Business Horizons, Inc., to
11 support commemorative and educational activities in conjunction with the 250th anniversary of
12 the signing of the Halifax Resolves."
13 SECTION 6. The Revisor of Statutes is authorized to alphabetize, number, and
14 renumber the special registration plates listed in G.S. 20-63(b1), 20-79.4(b), 20-79.7(a1) and (b),
15 and 20-81.12 to ensure that all the special registration plates are listed in alphabetical order and
16 numbered accordingly.
17 SECTION 7. This act is effective when it becomes law.
